notes.title: Author contributions
notes.p: S.W.M. and A.T. performed the majority of experiments. A.B., J.F., and M.J.M. expressed and purified ZIKV monomer and dimer proteins. C.A.L., H.M.L., and S.T. performed the animal experiments, S.W.M., S.T., and A.M.dS. designed the study. S.W.M. wrote the paper and all authors reviewed the paper.
